Usage: createLogicHierarchy [-help] -cell <string> [-commit] -newHinst <string>
                            [-objects <string>] [-selected]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>         # new cell name (string, required)
-commit                # commit group result (bool, optional)
-newHinst <string>     # new hier inst name (string, required)
-objects <string>      # Specifies list of hinst and/or instance groups
                       # (string, optional)
-selected              # specifies that grouping is done for the current
                       # selected hinsts or instant groups (bool, optional)